285/image.jpg 380w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/750/562/image.jpg 750w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1024/768/image.jpg 1024w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1372/1029/image.jpg 1372w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1536/1152/image.jpg 1536w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106255293/1920/1440/image.jpg 1920w" title="APT 101" width="750"/></picture></div><figcaption class="_figcaption_18vpl_1" data-testid="image-credits_testID"><span>Photograph: APT 101</span></figcaption></a></div><div class="_summaryContainer_osmln_364"><div class="_summary_osmln_21"><div class="_p_1mmxl_1" data-testid="summary_testID"><p><strong>What''s the vibe?</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"> APT 101 isn’t just a club; it’s a retro-inspired space that channels the glamour of 1970s New York with a Bangkok twist. Soft lighting, a crackling fireplace, and mid-century decor create a cosy yet stylish atmosphere perfect for unwinding. Inspired by RH, a legendary New York designer, the space is hosted by a mysterious figure who adds a layer of intrigue. Start your evening at the Pantry with sundowners from 6pm, a relaxed spot for after-work drinks and small plates, with live music setting the tone every Friday. Come May, the Arcade opens – a nostalgic room filled with vintage games and vinyl spinning all night. End your night at the Clubhouse, APT 101’s main stage, where disco house, afro house, and melodic beats keep the energy alive until late.</span></p>\n<p><strong>What to drink:</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Give crimson velvet (B400) a go – a deep, reddish-brown beauty that’s as bold, smooth and effortlessly stylish as a night spent grooving under the glittering lights.</span></p>\n<p><strong>When to visit: </strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"> When you fancy a trip to 1970s New York, but make it Bangkok.</span></p>\n<p><strong>APT 101, 3rd Floor, 233 Sukhumvit Rd (Corner of Soi 17), Khwaeng Khlong Toei Nuea, Watthana, Bang