iff, nodding to a finely curated set, and being grateful you remembered to wear leather. By midnight, it simmers. By two, it sizzles.</span></p></div></section><section class="_container_1qmjv_1" data-section-name="details"><div class="_title_1qmjv_5"><h3 class="_h3_1jrz3_1" data-testid="section-title_testID">Details</h3><div class="_wave_1v957_1 _wavyLine_1qmjv_10"></div></div><div class="_content_1qmjv_16"><div class="_mapWrap_1qmjv_51"><div class="_root_10dbg_1" data-component="maps" data-jwt="eyJraWQiOiIyNDgyRjZUN0JTIiwidHlwIjoiSldUIiwiYWxnIjoiRVMyNTYifQ.eyJpc3MiOiJKNERFOEVWODZVIiwiaWF0IjoxNzI0NjYzODEyLCJvcmlnaW4iOiIqLnRpbWVvdXQuY29tIn0.Ji3oznmRgvkDjSio5T4MgJcovZqbF4z-BIS7fWdjTc26Jt8le56mc5hBrCg2kk1Qwh0mLKUlefoKsgJ9JjiMog" data-testid="mapLite_testID" data-zone-location-info=''{"address1":"96 Naradhiwas Rajanagarindra Rd, Si Lom, Bang Rak","addressCity":"Bangkok","postcode":"10500","zones":[{"latitude":13.724152,"longitude":100.528688,"name":"BEAMCUBE"}]}''><div class="_map_10dbg_11" id="map"></div><div class="_toggleButton_10dbg_17" id="toggle-button" role="button"><div class="_root_1rydk_1" role="img"></div></div></div></div><div class="_info_1qmjv_43"><div class="_container_ofd8u_1" data-testid="details-info_testID"><div class="_details_ofd8u_5" data-section="details"><dl class="_list_ofd8u_52"><dt class="_term_ofd8u_66">Address</dt><dd class="_description_ofd8u_56">96 Naradhiwas Rajanagarindra Rd, Si Lom, Bang Rak</dd><dd class="_description_ofd8u_56">Bangkok</dd><dd class="_description_ofd8u_56">10500</dd></dl></div><div class="_details_ofd8u_5" data-section="openinghours"><dl class="_list_ofd8u_52"><dt class="_term_ofd8u_66">Opening hours:</dt><dd class="_description_ofd8u_56">Open Daily 5pm-2am</dd></dl></div><div class="_contactButtons_ofd8u_94"><div data-section="contact"><a class="_a_ofd8u_81" data-data-layer=''{"triggerOn":0,"payload":{"action":"link - external","label":"ev directions","category":"GP Engagement"}}'' href="https://www.google.com/maps/d