5/380/285/image.jpg 380w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/750/562/image.jpg 750w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/1024/768/image.jpg 1024w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/1372/1029/image.jpg 1372w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/1536/1152/image.jpg 1536w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/1920/1440/image.jpg 1920w" width="750"/></picture></a><div class="_articleContent_1j7tl_153"><a class="_imageLinkContainerSm_1j7tl_10" data-data-layer=''{"triggerOn":0,"payload":{"category":"GP Engagement","label":"in content","action":"link - internal"}}'' data-testid="tile-link_testID" href="/bangkok/things-to-do/queer-dance-wave-1" rel="" target="_self"><picture><source height="562" srcset="https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/380/285/image.webp 380w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/750/562/image.webp 750w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/1024/768/image.webp 1024w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/1372/1029/image.webp 1372w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/1536/1152/image.webp 1536w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/1920/1440/image.webp 1920w" type="image/webp" width="750"/><img class="_image_1j7tl_10 aspect-ratio-4-3" data-testid="responsive-image_testID" height="562" loading="lazy" sizes="auto" src="https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/750/562/image.jpg" srcset="https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/380/285/image.jpg 380w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/750/562/image.jpg 750w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/1024/768/image.jpg 1024w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/1372/1029/image.jpg 1372w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/1536/1152/image.jpg 1536w,https://media.timeout.com/images/106313775/1920/1440/image.jpg 1920w" width="750"/></picture></a><div class="_infoContainer_1j7tl_39"><a class="_title_1j7tl_50" data-data-layer=''{"triggerOn":0,"payload":{"category":"GP Engagement","label":"in content","action":"link - internal"}}'' data-testid="tile-link_testID" href="/bangkok/things-to-do/queer-dance-wave-1" rel="" target="_self"><h3>Queer Dance Wave</h3></a><div class="_summary_1j7tl_52 _p_1mmxl_1" data-testid="summary_testID">If you’re still catching your breath from the last Queer Dance Wave, brace yourself: it’s back, and this time the chaos spills across two rooms. At the centre is Paul Wolsch, a name whispered with a kind of reverence in Central America’s queer electronic underground. A longtime resident at Guatemala City’s Club Vertigo, he’s also the mind behind collectives with names as audacious as their parties – GAG, SPUNK and WARP Festival. His sets are less performance than pilgrimage, stitched together from vinyl that slides between house, techno and acid with unnerving precision. It’s classical in its architecture, filthy in its energy, and just the right amount of unpredictable. Add Bangkok’s own crowd into the mix and you’ve got the makings of a delirious night.\nSeptember 6. B400-450 via here and B500-600 at the door. Beamcube, 6pm onwards</div><section class="_tileTags_1j7tl_53 _tags_1i2cm_17" data-testid="tags_testID"><ul class="_tagsList_1i2cm_17"><li class="_tagBare_1i2cm_27 _tagComponent_1i2cm_63"><div class="_tagContainer_1bfie_8" data-testid="event-details_testID"><span class="_tag_1bfie_8 _dateTag_1bfie_1"><time class="_time_1wpy4_1" datetime="2025-09-06T18:00:00+07:00">Sep 6, 2025</time></span></div></li></ul></section></div></div></article></div></section></section><aside class="_side_content_xppf9_8"><div class="_side_wrap_xppf9_61 _side_wrap_bottom_xppf9_66"><div class="stickyContainer" data-testid="side-ads-container_testID"></div><div class="stickyContainer" data-testid="side-ads-container_testID"></div></div></aside><section class="_full_content_xppf9_27"><div data-component="taboola-mobile-widget" data-testid="taboola-mobile-widget_testID"><div class="_container_fb8kb_1 _hide_fb8kb_6"><div id="taboola-mobile-below-article-thumbnails"></div></div></div><di