ph: Golden State Vegan Bangkok </span></figcaption></figure></div></div><h1 class="_articleTitle_5sxtq_27 _h1_1myhj_1" data-testid="article-title_testID">Golden State Vegan</h1><section class="_heroTags_5sxtq_6 _tags_1i2cm_17" data-testid="tags_testID"><ul class="_tagsList_1i2cm_17"><li class="_tag_1i2cm_17"><span class="_text_1i2cm_68">Restaurants</span></li><li class="_tag_1i2cm_17"><span class="_text_1i2cm_68">Phrom Phong</span></li></ul></section><div class="_publishedDateContainer_5sxtq_63 _articleDateContainer_1wzx7_1 _whiteWhite_1wzx7_8" data-testid="publish_date_with_image_credits"><time class="_articleTime_1wpy4_12" datetime="2025-04-17T00:00:00+07:00">Thursday April 17 2025</time></div><div class="_container_4pch7_1" data-component="sharing-links"><input class="_input_4pch7_6" id="sharing-buttons-cta" name="sharing-buttons" type="checkbox"/><label class="_label_4pch7_35 _whiteWhite_4pch7_14" for="sharing-buttons-cta"><svg class="" viewbox="0 0 32 32" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M28 16v5.6c0 2.24 0 3.36-.436 4.216a4 4 0 0 1-1.748 1.748C24.96 28 23.84 28 21.6 28H10.4c-2.24 0-3.36 0-4.216-.436a4 4 0 0 1-1.748-1.748C4 24.96 4 23.84 4 21.6V16m17.333-6.667L16 4m0 0-5.333 5.333M16 4v16" fill-rule="evenodd" stroke="#E1192C" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.1"></path></svg></label></div></section><section class="_container_1lq4t_1" data-section-name="review"><div class="_title_1lq4t_10"><h3 class="_h3_1jrz3_1" data-testid="section-title_testID">Time Out says</h3><div class="_wave_1v957_1 _wavyLine_1lq4t_32"></div></div><div class="_content_1t3mx_1 contentAnnotation" data-component="annotation" data-testid="annotation_testID" id="content"><p><strong>What is it?: </strong><span>A Japanese/Californian fusion restaurant with a cocktail bar and DJ deck that gets livelier by the hour as the evening progresses.</span></p>\n<p><strong>Why we love it?: </strong><span>No artificial meats are used and the sauces are all imagined i