INSERT INTO places VALUES(309,'bk_magazine','https://bk.asia-city.com/nightlife/article/bangkoks-best-rooftop-bars#Bar.Yard','<article>Bar.Yard</article>','2025-09-06 11:35:17.687783',13.737457399999999374,100.54380109999998538,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Bar.Yard',NULL,'Bar.Yard should be no stranger to folks who know Bangkok’s nightlife scene or fans of rooftop bars. This is the third year in a row the venue has earned the top spot from the BAD Awards voting panel in the rooftop bar category, and that’s largely because the venue keeps refining its best-in-class formula. This year, it launched an all-new line-up of weekly parties called “Nights at the Yard”, creating a good mixture of vibes and energy levels here with everything from ladies nights to more off-the-cuff parties and cosmopolitan dance-offs. Combine that with the already good food and drink and you have a home run yet again.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'new',NULL,NULL,'2025-09-17 04:33:42',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO places VALUES(310,'bk_magazine','https://bk.asia-city.com/nightlife/article/bangkoks-best-rooftop-bars#Nobu_Rooftop','<article>Nobu Rooftop</article>','2025-09-06 11:35:17.693701',13.720467999999998998,100.53014679999998648,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Nobu Rooftop',NULL,'Nobu Bangkok was one of the most highly anticipated openings of 2024, commanding a large media junket and acting as the main promotional vehicle for the larger EA Rooftop launch at the top of Empire Tower. While the restaurant takes up most of the limelight, the open-air rooftop bar area has quietly stolen the show, and our panelists agreed. Completely booked nearly every night, what the bar area lacks in raw mixologist firepower it more than makes up for with some of the most insane 360-degree views you find in the city.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'new',NULL,NULL,'2025-09-17 04:33:42',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO places VALUES(311,'bk_magazine','https://bk.asia-city.com/nightlife/article/bangkoks-best-rooftop-bars#Finalist:_Penthouse_Bar_+_Grill','<article>Finalist: Penthouse Bar + Grill</article>','2025-09-06 11:35:17.696877',13.743898000000001058,100.54705999999999921,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Finalist: Penthouse Bar + Grill',NULL,'ThreeSixty Rooftop BarPhoto: ThreeSixty Rooftop Bar / FacebookPerched on the 32nd floor of the Millennium Hilton, ThreeSixty Rooftop Bar lives up to its name with sweeping 360-degree views over the Chao Phraya River that are hard to match. Whether you''re lounging near the helipad or tucked into one of the sofas under the stars, it’ll be hard to match the vibes here on this side of the river. The sunset scene pairs well with a French 75—a crisp mix of gin, lemon, and sparkling wine—or the Grand Cosmopolitan, made with Absolut Elyx and Grand Marnier for a smooth, citrus-forward sip. The classic cocktail list covers all the bases, and a solid Champagne selection will help you turn up the celebration when needed. DJs, garden accents, and a cool-as-hell helipad help to take this rooftop spot over the edge. ThreeSixty Rooftop Bar,  Millennium Hilton Bangkok, 123 Charoen Nakhon Rd, .  daily 5pm-1am.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'new',NULL,NULL,'2025-09-17 04:33:42',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO places VALUES(312,'bk_magazine','https://bk.asia-city.com/nightlife/article/bangkoks-best-rooftop-bars#Finalist:_Com’On_Bar','<article>Finalist: Com’On Bar</article>','2025-09-06 11:35:17.699887',13.739951999999999721,100.51782099999999608,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Finalist: Com’On Bar',NULL,'One of the youngest entries to crack this list in years, opening in just 2023, Com’On Bar’s location just on the outskirts of the city’s old town keeps it far away from the gleaming high rises of the business districts, allowing its perch on the seventh floor to offer 270-degree views of the surrounding area, which the bar team gives nods too through their area-themed drinks like the smoky-flavored “Old Town” the housing number of the building with the crisp “One One Four”. A respectable selection of craft beers on tap rounds out the menu.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'new',NULL,NULL,'2025-09-17 04:33:42',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO places VALUES(313,'bk_magazine','https://bk.asia-city.com/nightlife/article/bangkoks-best-rooftop-bars#ThreeSixty_Rooftop_Bar','<article>ThreeSixty Rooftop Bar</article>','2025-09-06 11:35:17.702832',13.728800199999999787,100.51131330000000474,NULL,NULL,NULL,'ThreeSixty Rooftop Bar',NULL,'Head up to Bangkok’s sky-high Peruvian-Japanese rooftop restaurant and bar in Bangkok for panoramic sunset views, zesty pisco sours, and innovative fusion cocktails. They provide Nikkei food, a combination of Peruvian and Japanese cuisine, so be sure to try the ceviche sampling plate, tacos, or the South American grilled platter. The rooftop''s sleek and fashionable design draws inspiration from Central Park in New York City, and the space is outfitted with artificial grass, wooden structure trees, neon blue and pink lights, a maze, and, to top it all off, a bathroom with a view of the Bangkok cityscape.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'new',NULL,NULL,'2025-09-17 04:33:42',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
